Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玉木同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麼看 鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}挺平常的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}關冰箱門的聲音一如往常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}切菜的節奏也沒什麼異常的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}平常過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彷彿是不想讓我們察覺才演出來似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我買了入浴劑 幫我拿進洗澡間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近新出這款呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老媽已經全知道了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對 可能只是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不能自亂陣腳跳進陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但要是老媽真知道了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我繼續隱瞞 只會讓情勢更加不利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我應該積極點…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了 還是有什麼心事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}關於南極…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:04:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽…媽媽 其實我冬天要去那邊旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來已經決定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽都被蒙在鼓裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是今天聽鄰居說了才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽真沒面子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實我就準備告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是之前沒好的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想等到確定了再說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是誰簽的名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰蓋的章呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慢著 慢著 慢著 慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你先放下武器 有話好說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不是武器 是湯勺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過拿蠢女兒煮湯 也能派上用場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼講話跟鬼婆婆一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.40,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女兒 爸爸對不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:54.87,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}錯都錯在小理你自己身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別一句話作結嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之後我要是有一科不及格就不能去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}集訓期間本來就沒空念書的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你下週真要請假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 算上週末一共四天 所以要請假到週二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我查過 還沒確定會不會發船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在想那種事也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我得去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別累壞自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是拼了命努力也沒成功 你會很懊悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說啊 你讀了高中就有上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是你每天有很多時間可以認真學習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是還學不好 肯定是你花的心思不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且學習不像體育 只要下功夫就會有收穫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也是敵軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼友軍敵軍的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是說日向說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了 人家去找結月求援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她比你小耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnGen Jyuu Gothic Bold\bord0\fs30\1c&H32383A&\fscy20\t(0,100,0\fscy100)\pos(622,96)}我出檢票口了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她說到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}氣場好像不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前有工作在身 只能那麼穿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能那麼穿？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不適合那種可愛的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺跟我的性格不搭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得挺可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我不喜歡被人看成是那種小女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她怎麼不高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想想她的工作 肯定有不少酸甜苦辣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有走錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 這裡不太好找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來 上車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我馬上收拾下 對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:24.10,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs60\1vc(&H8291B0&,&H8291B0&,&H9DD03E&,&H9DD03E&)\fn華康POP1體W9\pos(690,590)\frx44\fry30\frz17.45}南極\N{\1vc(&HA73533&,&HA73533&,&H77299D&,&H77299D&)}挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像…跟想像中不太一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟你們想像的不同嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「南極觀測隊」聽起來像個大計畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是民間組織
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不會開這種破舊的小廂型車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該怎麼接話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過我沒想到你真的會跟我們同行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那一百萬元呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道你要那些錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就如報導上寫的 我們沒什麼錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:12.94,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康中特圓體\fs25\frz282\1c&H1F2325&\3c&H87AABF&\move(798,406,702,406,0,7000)}別放錄音帶\N危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為去南極的費用已經花了很大一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以其他能砍掉的開銷就砍乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過你們放心 不至於中止的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:22.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\p1\fscx2000\fscy2200\1c&HAEB8B4&\1a&H50&\pos(216,254)}m -10 10 l -10 -10 l 10 -10 l 10 10
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:22.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\an5\fn華康楷書體W5\bord0\1c&H3D403F&\fs25\pos(192,76)}民間日本南極觀測隊\N「南極挑戰（第二次）」\N招募贊助事項
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:22.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\fn華康楷書體W5\bord0\1c&H474949&\fs20\pos(26,138)}敬啟 祝收到材料的貴社發展順利\N\N此次由「南極挑戰」組織的，時隔三年的第\N二次民間南極觀測隊，幸運地得到了派遣南\N極的機會。\N\N如今，地球環境問題極其嚴峻，南極蘊藏的\N科學價值更加得到關注，南極觀測項目也肩\N負起了更重要的意義。\N\N此次「南極挑戰」觀測項目，是我們懷著為\N人類的未來做貢獻的決心，計劃在世界寶貴\N的共同財富—南極上，開展的全球性活動。\N\N因此，請恕我們提出此次申請，希望貴社能\N夠理解此次項目的宗旨，並通過贊助為這個\N計畫盡一份力。\N\N有關贊助的內容見下文，還請不吝一閱。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們幾個可能不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個計畫從出來後 就一直備受輿論
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:24.53,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fn華康POP1體W7\1c&H24364A&\3c&H3F4B4B&\fs30\shad3\frz349.2\frx320\fry348\move(206,192,214,156,0,1914)}破冰船白瀨號\N\N{\shad0\1c&H9CADA5&\3c&H3D402B&}招募命名權夥伴{\fsp-15}！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:24.53,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\an5\fn華康儷中黑\fs30\1c&HAFB6AA&\3c&H3D4133&\frx322\fry358\frz345.9\move(276,384,284,352,0,1914)}您提的名字會塗在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:24.53,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3C403D&\frz348.9\move(892,492,892,450,0,1914)}徽章
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總被批評資金不足 危險性高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每當碰上這種報導
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就會拉上其他成員去對方辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要你廢話 蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們也一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是山區吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.86,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到是到了 但要等到後天才能外出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今明兩天都得上課
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:03.40,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康隸書體W7\bord0\fs50\1c&H6D7A78&\frz261.5\frx2\fry10\move(496,290,598,290,0,3997)}百名山旅店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 快進去快進去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先看一下資料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厲害 是基地導覽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}內部資料 小心保管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:15.26,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs45\frz338.9\1c&H273738&\t(0,2540,0\fs35)\move(764,66,874,56,41,2502)}現在的昭和基地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:15.26,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs40\1c&H192E31&\t(0,2540,0\fs30)\frz347.6\frx354\fry0\move(88,612,360,474,41,2502)}新基地建設
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:15.26,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs40\1c&H192E31&\t(0,2540,0\fs30)\frx354\fry0\frz337.7\move(654,672,734,574,35,1662)}極地越冬隊的住處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雪地車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有點熱血沸騰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:17.51,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\1c&H93A3A1&\3&H2E2722&c\frz15.49\frx334\fry358\move(14,160,184,160,34,2244)}發現大量隕石的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:17.51,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\1c&H362971&\frz15.49\frx344\fry2\move(392,146,556,146,34,2244)}世界屈指可數的隕石儲備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:17.51,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs20\1c&H232829&\frz17.03\frx352\fry0\move(514,366,676,364,0,2244)}日本迄今找到了17,100顆隕石，擁有世界屈指可數的隕石儲備。\N共有9顆{\1c&H3F3776&}火星隕石{\1c&H232829&}，9顆{\1c&H3F3776&}月球隕石{\1c&H232829&}。\N(參考)美國17,301顆，中國9,836顆，韓國21顆，\N\h\h\h\h\h\h其他各國(含歐洲)869顆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以那份資料為基礎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下來你們四位將接受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等同其他隊員冬夏兩季受過的訓練的濃縮版課程
