Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}# 南極條約特徵 *南極洲僅用於和平目的 *自由進行科學調查和促進國際間合作 *凍結領土主權的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那裡和日本不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有許多制度和規則
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}趁這次集訓好好記在心裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟學校裡的你判若兩人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們又不同班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼首先和隊長打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是南極觀測隊隊長藤堂吟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是女性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}醜話說在前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管隊員是隨行人員還是研究人員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都一視同仁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要做的事堆積如山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你們是高中生 只要有需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無論掃地 洗衣服 苦力活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們一個都別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把我的話記清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極觀測隊員有個ABC準則
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A.這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}B.別做傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}C.打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請把這三點謹記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:44.09,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\1c&H3D423E&\frz20.47\frx358\fry356\pos(336,92)}１．想活下去\N\N２．想知道更多\N\N３．想扶持隊友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:44.09,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\1c&H3D423E&\frx4\fry0\frz18.24\pos(-4,400)}全部符合南極觀測隊。無論如何都要活下去、生還下來。\N保持對知識和經驗的渴求。另外，不要孤立你的隊友。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她好有隊長風範啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像那種看到學生打瞌睡 就會扔粉筆的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是有考試 都是出超難的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了 明天是訓練開路工程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 要去外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都來山裡了 不出去走走就可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過這工程看來挺辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久違的再會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說了 對所有隊員一視同仁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是故意的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒 我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那孩子是靠自己來到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過說實話 我早有預感了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從她第一次跟我說想一起去的時候起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她可是貴子的女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是收發器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個是指南針
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後這個是GPS定位裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有旗子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向弄懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨天基本上都教過了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是為什麼要做這些事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極是塊平整的大陸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用開路也能走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為是平整又純白的大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一旦下暴風雪就會迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才要開路 方便沿著路走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怪不得要插這個旗子當路標
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是要插在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是要我們自己想 才有這個訓練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:34.22,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frx350\fry6\pos(768,156)\frz19.15}開路工程起點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:34.22,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frx350\fry6\pos(466,116)\frz20.46}通訊基地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:34.22,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H3C3F40&\frx350\fry6\frz23.13\pos(244,446)}下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是我們目前的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:39.83,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frz19.15\pos(586,246)\frx348\fry356}開路工程路線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:39.83,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frx348\fry356\frz25.21\pos(80,244)}開路工程終點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:39.83,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frx348\fry356\frz25.21\pos(350,652)}野營訓練地點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後這邊是目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到那裡去就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不單單是過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}途中的這裡 這裡和這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這些地點都要插上旗子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別那麼隨隨便便就行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道那些地點在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}…哎嘿？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}賣萌也沒有用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用這個一邊測量正確的地點一邊前進
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺會很難耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}48 49 50
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看一下角度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用右眼看還是左眼看？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是慣用眼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慣用眼是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我記得是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}168°
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再向右一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}右？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}右
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個右邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}緯度是這個 經度是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是不是比剛才的距離更遠啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果測量正確的話 應該在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那邊嗎…偏了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想起來自己當初剛參加時的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其他三個人是怎麼進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不清楚 其中一個原本就要參加的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知什麼時候她們變成朋友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其他隊員說要爭取時間越短越好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我覺得準確度比速度更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟安全第一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}398 399 400
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}向左兩步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過你居然知道小理很會用指南針啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是個直覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請叫我指南針的專家—「指南針女孩」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了 我是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像畢業旅行一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不打個牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又不是來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在帳篷裡睡覺也是重要的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是現在還不到8點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想 隊長也說合宿的晚上要開聯歡會的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 快給我睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來聊聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}講鬼故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有點想殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道結月害怕鬼故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死請靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:10.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※結月本想説うるさい（吵死了），但這個詞對學姐講很沒禮貌，臨時改口說\N\h\h\h\h静かにしてください（請保持安靜），結果把兩個不相干的詞組在了一起。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死請靜是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看你是學姐我才臨時改口的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道我想表達什麼意思就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死請靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別說啦 小理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨 睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直想問個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨 你認識隊長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼會這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:16:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個人是媽媽高中時的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和媽媽一起去了南極
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個人回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有媽媽沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為 媽媽還等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}滿天繁星 北極星是哪一顆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是在北斗七星某段的延長線上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟仙后座有關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那南極星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極星？有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有倒是有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是不明顯 比較難找到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從這裡是看不到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要以為自己頭頂上的群星就是全部的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是日向的名言吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}編得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是昭和基地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}極光隊能聽到嗎 請回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是極光隊 我是三宅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}信號良好 請回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是定時聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有沒有異常 請回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本日 極光隊4名成員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人員設備均無異常 請回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}破曉時溫度較低 注意保暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}定時聯絡結束 祝一切安好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}祝一切安好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好險 差點忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:57.70,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H403533&\pos(442,280)\frz18.96}新訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:57.70,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs40\1c&H726257&\frz18.96\pos(392,354)\frx348\fry350}收件人：{\1c&H403533&}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:57.70,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs40\1c&H726257&\frz18.96\frx348\fry350\pos(548,506)}主旨：{\1c&H403533&}致媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請問
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨的媽媽是怎樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我只能回答你 她是個怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像報瀨那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道 我不清楚她女兒是什麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過她們的執著與死心眼 倒是像極了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真夠麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:26.53,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}深夜零時の地平線　広がる世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:30.99,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}今日がずっと眩しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:41.76,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}鼻の奥がツンとした　きれいできれいで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:46.41,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}胸が痛くなるほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:56.00,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}両手いっぱいありったけの人に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:21:06.62,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}意味なんかないって言われ続けたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:19.18,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}宇宙(そら)から届くひかり　逆さまの星空見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:23.21,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}ここから始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:31.75,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}さあ　迷いなんて置き去りにして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:38.38,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}探しに行くんだ　見果てぬ世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:47.02,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}さあ前を向いて　間違いなかったんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:53.38,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}言ってやるんだ　この思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:22:01.83,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}勇気出して　進んでいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:26.53,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}眼前是深夜零點的地平線 一片廣大的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:30.99,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}今天一直是那麼耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:41.76,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我激動得鼻尖一癢 眼前的景象是那麼美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:46.41,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}燦爛到叫我心口作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:56.00,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}許許多多的人 裝滿雙手也擠不下的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:21:06.62,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}都在勸我不要白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:19.18,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}只是仰頭看見那顛倒的星空 灑下的星光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:23.21,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我會從這裡揚帆起航
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:31.75,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}把心裡的迷茫留在岸邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:38.38,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}去探索廣闊無垠 斑斕神秘的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:47.02,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}睜大眼睛直視前方 大聲喊出
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:53.38,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}「我的執著沒有錯誤！」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:22:01.83,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}拿出勇氣 走出大大的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但麻煩點才好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的性格很適合去南極
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼要去南極
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被她叫來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是下決心的是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想和她一起去 不想就這樣虛度高中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想去見識不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過認識了日向和結月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了觀測隊隊員的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽了隊長和報瀨的事情後 我才覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是哪裡都好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:20:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而是非南極不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想和大家一起去南極
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早起很難受的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了快起來 還有報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快點來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想和大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想和大家一起找到南極星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看極光 吃刨冰 和企鵝拍紀念照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們一定要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Comment: 0,0:22:05.04,0:22:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:25.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}長いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.27,0:22:36.81,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:42.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}間違っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:53.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　僕は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:23:04.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}汚れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:15.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言葉も　きっと見つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:21.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:26.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:25.89,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}尋找著漫長隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.27,0:22:36.81,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向著泛著微光氣味的方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:42.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走錯了 也別忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:53.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}從這裡開始 我將踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:23:04.13,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}緊緊捏住手心裡 髒髒的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:15.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}沒說出口的話 我也一定會找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:21.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}隨你們嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:26.35,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 邁出腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:38.07,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H8AA4A0&\pos(234,68)\frz13.84}好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:38.07,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H838D8B&\frz13.84\pos(662,660)}這裡很美吧？
